headline: Crocs Q4: Post-Earnings 20% Rally Is Just The Beginning
summary: Crocs' FY24 revenues grew by 3.1%, driven by its Crocs brand, while HEYDUDE brand saw its revenue coming in flat YoY. See why I'm reiterating buy rating on CROX.
